Package: RemoveUnwantedVariance
Type: Package
Title: Remove Unwanted Variation from High-Throughput Genomic Data
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Songchen Yang [aut, cre]
Description: A toolkit for identifying and removing unwanted technical/biological variation from high-throughput genomic data, particularly RNA-Seq datasets. Implements robust normalization methods using housekeeping genes to correct for batch effects and other biological variation, enabling more accurate downstream differential expression analysis.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    stats,
    utils,
    tidyverse,
    limma,
    sva,
    DESeq2
Suggests: 
